OL,3,CGovernment plans more benefit cuts as
OL,4,COBR downgrades welfare savings
OL,6,FSources tell me that Chancellor Rachel
OL,7,FReeves will now cut an extra #500
OL,8,Fmillion by freezing incapacity
OL,9,Fbenefits (the higher rate of universal
OL,10,Fcredit) until 2030 after an initial
OL,11,Fcut, and will also slightly reduce the
OL,12,Fbasic rate of universal credit in 2029
OL,13,Fafter an earlier increase.
OL,15,FThe figure comes from #4.8 billion in
OL,16,Fterms of the gross amount raised, but
OL,17,Fwith #1 billion going into employment
OL,18,Fsupport, and then more into other
OL,19,Fparts of the reform.
