OL,6,FAnd could the plans still hit one
OL,7,Fmillion disabled people, but save less
OL,8,Fmoney? That is the worry of some
OL,9,Fsenior figures I've spoken to.
OL,11,FI've heard that the OBR's difference
OL,12,Fwith the government is over how the
OL,13,FPersonal Independence Payment (Pip)
OL,14,Fassessors will behave, with an
OL,15,Fexpectation that more people will
OL,16,Flikely pass the new tougher tests than
OL,17,Fgovt officials believe.
